# ▶️ How to Run

1. Clone the repository.

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
```

2. Install the required libraries.

```bash
pip install pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn scikit-learn shap
```

3. Open the notebook.

```
customer_churn_analysis.ipynb
```

4. Run all cells.

